    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>A university in Edinburgh is developing a short online taster course for people interested in developing careers in dispute resolution and conflict management.</p>
<p>Conflict arises in many contexts – at work, at home, and in personal relationships. Queen Margaret University (QMU), Edinburgh will run a free online taster course which will provide an insight into how conflict can be resolved. It will cover topics such as ‘understanding conflict, ‘conflict escalation’ and ‘resolving conflict’.</p>]]></Value>
